## Backend environment variables

## Database
# Local development (MongoDB running locally)
# MONGO_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/swigato
# Production (MongoDB Atlas)
MONGO_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/swigato

## Authentication
# JWT secret for token generation (CHANGE THIS FOR PRODUCTION!)
JWT_SECRET=change_me_in_production

# Bcrypt salt rounds (recommended: 10)
SALT=10

## Stripe Configuration (REQUIRED for payments)
# Get these from https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_xxxxxxxxxxxx
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_xxxxxxxxxxxx

## Frontend URL (CRITICAL for Stripe redirects)
# Local development
# FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173
# Production
# FRONTEND_URL=https://your-frontend-url.vercel.app
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173
